> Meteara: Magnificient! This was a worthy demonstration! Perhaps even
> worthy of some beings more powerful than the Cybertronians!
> Now, I need to discuss with the one who is in charge of this group.
> There are great things going on, and I need the cooperation of anyone
> who can help me.
>

{Talos}

    Talos looked up from the energon realizing his mistake in his orders and
sighed. This day had simply been to hectic. "Maximals, back to base!"
Turning he looked upon Meteara. "I'm commander of the maximals on this
mission what can I do for you?"

    He turned more fully to face the bot tucking the blast sheild he was
carrying onto a hitch at his back, ignoring the dark glare Grimlock cast his
way even as the metallic dinobot stomped back towards the maximal ship.
